  "prompt": "What are the symptoms of anxiety?",
  "response": "Anxiety can manifest through various physical, emotional, and behavioral symptoms:\n\nPhysical symptoms:\n1. Rapid heartbeat\n2. Sweating\n3. Trembling or shaking\n4. Shortness of breath\n5. Chest pain\n6. Muscle tension\n7. Fatigue\n8. Digestive issues\n9. Headaches\n10. Dizziness\n\nEmotional symptoms:\n1. Persistent worry\n2. Feeling restless or on edge\n3. Difficulty concentrating\n4. Irritability\n5. Sense of impending doom\n6. Feeling overwhelmed\n7. Excessive fear\n8. Panic attacks\n9. Sleep disturbances\n10. Low self-esteem\n\nBehavioral symptoms:\n1. Avoiding social situations\n2. Procrastination\n3. Seeking constant reassurance\n4. Difficulty making decisions\n5. Overanalyzing scenarios\n6. Withdrawal from activities\n7. Compulsive behaviors\n8. Difficulty maintaining relationships\n9. Perfectionism\n10. Increased use of substances\n\nIf these symptoms persist or significantly impact daily life, consulting a mental health professional is recommended.",
